This repository uses a per-directory license split.

License mapping:

- `sources/driver/` and `sources/patches/`: `GPL-2.0-only`
- userspace helper scripts and daemons under `sources/`: `MIT`
- documentation (`*.md` and similar repository docs): `CC-BY-4.0`

Third-party material:

- `prebuilt/` artifacts remain under their original upstream licenses
- reference source material and archived research notes remain under their original upstream licenses unless a file states otherwise

Canonical license texts:

- GPL-2.0-only: https://spdx.org/licenses/GPL-2.0-only.html
- MIT: https://spdx.org/licenses/MIT.html
- CC-BY-4.0: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

When a file carries its own SPDX identifier or license notice, that file-level notice controls.